Wesley Central Hall, Portsmouth 2nd annual contest organised by the Portsmouth City Fire Brigade Prize Band
British Bandsman 23-9-1950 gives results as - Section 1 Test piece AKHNATON - 1st Morris Motors H.Mortimer, 2nd Hoo Silver Eric Ball, 3rd High Wycombe Town Phil Catelinet. Section 2 'The VIKING'; 1st Fishponds B.L. 2nd Bitterne and West End, 3rd Chippenham Silver. Held at Wesley Central Hall, Fratton Road,Southsea.
Brass Band News October 1950 gives the same result as you have given, 5 bands competed in open section, 6 bands competed in section 2.
